{"tid":403683,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"吳 業 坤 晒 拉 麵 絕 技","createTime":"2017-09-17T11:42:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-17T13:24:21.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4beec17c05c6a7385e61fdfebb8ce291124ae99d","tid":403683,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T11:42:56.000Z","msg":"歌手吳業坤一向都係以實力取勝，之前仲喺《IFPI香港唱片銷量大獎2016》橫掃咗四個大獎，近期佢就忙於喺內地拍攝劇集，但係佢都不忘喺社交網站同一班粉絲分享佢嘅近況。呢日佢就喺社交網站上載咗一段玩拉麵嘅影片，並留言：「其實我是一個拉面（麵）師傅」身穿圍裙嘅吳業坤，手上就拎咗一舊拉長咗嘅麵團，而且仲不停咁將麵團揈嚟揈去，連經過嘅店員都忍唔住望咗一眼。唔少網民都話好犀利，仲問曾經開過日式拉麵店嘅吳業坤係咪打算轉行去做拉麵師父添！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170915/photo/bkn-20170915085442578-0915_00862_001_01b.jpg?20170915101859\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170915%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170915085442578-0915_00862_001_01b.jpg%3F20170915101859&h=be74a1a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4203015b7ddf6c5f7afb26fe410002e25f383aaf","tid":403683,"uid":69038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T11:44:32.000Z","msg":"轉行啦"},{"pid":"dab70ff048eb8b838733374cbef4386672e47f3d","tid":403683,"uid":67903,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T11:49:15.000Z","msg":"唔怪得之面皮咁厚..."},{"pid":"47a425dd1d7a76e2b4ef5704c738fed779ab1892","tid":403683,"uid":27256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T13:00:54.000Z","msg":"維穩show演出喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23e72a3bc89bceeef446e9d9fd1fd8170dd51e77","tid":403683,"uid":80503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T13:02:08.000Z","msg":"髮線仲係咁高"},{"pid":"990e372feab4db15ba1baac5b1539bc78c0e3a5f","tid":403683,"uid":70391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T13:24:21.000Z","msg":"第一句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}